of piles. - & have used galvanic
circles [insertion]constructed with common sulphate of iron[/insertion] on which the pairs of metals
are either Zinc plates & silver or
iron wires: The great advantage
of circles are that you can interpose
a great number of bodies which
you wish to act chemically
upon in different part of the
circle -
